SUMMARY:Artist Talk and Reception with Linda Clark Johnson
DESCRIPTION:Artist Talk & Reception with Linda Clark Johnson in Davis \nSunday\, May 17\, 1-2:30 PM \nFree Admission \nJoin artist Linda Clark Johnson as she discusses her artistic process in working with cyanotype\, including her love of sunlight and her ways of gathering and arranging plants. Linda will also show visitors how to get started with cyanotype through an artist demo\, as well as explore her current work in her exhibit\, Sunshine & Shadows\, on view at the Pence Gallery from May 2 – June 21\, 2026.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/artist-talk-and-reception-with-linda-clark-johnson/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Linda-Clark-Johnson-MBuhzM.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencesocialmedia@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
